    <string name="terms_content">
        <![CDATA[
        <b>1. Acceptance of Terms</b>\n\n
        By registering as a driver, you agree to comply with all terms and conditions set forth by our platform.\n\n

        <b>2. Driver Requirements</b>\n\n
        • You must possess a valid driving license\n
        • Your vehicle must have valid insurance\n
        • You must maintain all documents up to date\n
        • You must be at least 18 years of age\n\n

        <b>3. Code of Conduct</b>\n\n
        • Maintain professional behavior with passengers\n
        • Keep your vehicle clean and well-maintained\n
        • Follow all traffic rules and regulations\n
        • Do not discriminate against any passenger\n\n

        <b>4. Document Verification</b>\n\n
        All uploaded documents will be verified by our team. Providing false information may result in account suspension or legal action.\n\n

        <b>5. Data Privacy</b>\n\n
        Your personal information will be kept confidential and used only for service-related purposes in accordance with our Privacy Policy.\n\n

        <b>6. Commission and Payments</b>\n\n
        • Platform commission will be deducted from each ride\n
        • Payments will be processed within 7 business days\n
        • You are responsible for any applicable taxes\n\n

        <b>7. Account Suspension</b>\n\n
        We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account for violation of these terms or inappropriate conduct.\n\n

        <b>8. Liability</b>\n\n
        You are responsible for any damages or incidents occurring during rides. Ensure adequate insurance coverage.\n\n

        <b>9. Updates to Terms</b>\n\n
        We may update these terms periodically. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of updated terms.\n\n

        <b>10. Contact</b>\n\n
        For any questions or concerns, please contact our support team.\n\n

        By checking the box below, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions.
        ]]>
